273
00:12:32,026 --> 00:12:35,840
I think Lady Buttons of Camelot has a
real shot in the progression ring today.

274
00:12:35,896 --> 00:12:38,472
Look at her.
She's having a really good fur day.

275
00:12:38,528 --> 00:12:40,431
Okay, I'm not dating
your kid anymore,

276
00:12:40,486 --> 00:12:42,750
so I don't have to listen
to all the cat chat.

277
00:12:42,807 --> 00:12:43,801
Marc's right.

278
00:12:43,858 --> 00:12:46,432
You are cranky when
you don't get your fix.

279
00:12:51,798 --> 00:12:54,142
Oh, look at this.

280
00:12:54,197 --> 00:12:55,933
It's Betty's papi.

281
00:12:55,986 --> 00:12:57,580
You should really talk to him.

282
00:12:57,636 --> 00:12:58,942
Won't Betty mind?

283
00:12:58,997 --> 00:13:02,280
